  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Git流程图，展示双向合并的场景。标题就叫\"Two-way merges\"，方向用从上到下（top-to-bottom）。核心是想表达main分支和develop分支之间来回merge的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph",
        "TB",
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，top-to-bottom布局。那初始结构我理解为：先有一个commit在main上，然后从main切出develop分支，develop上再做一个commit，是这样吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。然后切回main，把develop合并进来，这是第一次merge。接着main上再做一个commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一次merge和main上的commit都画好了。现在develop那边要做什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "然后切到develop，把main合并进来，这是反向的merge。之后develop再做一个commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：develop先merge main，然后再commit？这个顺序没问题吧，develop上的新commit是在合并之后？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "merge main",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，顺序没错。最后一步：切回main，再把develop合并进来，形成完整的双向合并闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "merge develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。图里现在清晰展示了main和develop之间三次关键merge：main←develop、develop←main、最后main←develop，双向流动一目了然。",
